{"tid":2040874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BE WATER 剋死林鄭+習近平","createTime":"2020-05-29T01:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T03:58:06.000Z","uid":32722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0ee216954b5d45b1e1ce2b46b0f95847c594f7","tid":2040874,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"之前去睇流年, 同師傅傾開習近平同林鄭命格非常忌水<br />\n所以佢一早話庚子年呢兩條友會好難捱<br />\n當時聽到都不以為然, 始終冇諗過一個武肺會搞到咁<br />\n但而家諗返, 黑色五行屬水, 連豬=亥年=水, BE WATER當然係水<br />\n可能有D野係整定, 呢幾樣抗爭完素+庚子年一獲搞到習近平犯下大錯<br />\n咁大家識點做啦?<br />\n<br />\n繼續擴大黃色經濟圈, 要令全港都貼滿連豬, 日日著黑色邪爆林鄭同習近平<br />\n最最最重要係大家要謹守BE WATER, 唔好死磨難磨, 屋企好多時都要人!"},{"pid":"f297695e170411fbf0386b392aa89acf787ca944","tid":2040874,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T01:20:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以無法為有法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4298e51a09fc73a1dea97993f1bd28a492b90e6c","tid":2040874,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725138407cc530fb4830a84c39ce82ab1f9d595a","tid":2040874,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"樓豬講起風水，我都講下啦<br />\n<br />\n見好多人都會留意黑色=水，水亦剋火<br />\n但好少人留意風水入面黃色=土，而火生土<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFDkpqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFDkpqv.jpg&h=ca931103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁可以解釋點解支那係咁壓住香港黎砌<br />\n但就越黎越多示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7z5CrEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7z5CrEU.jpg&h=a35190bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外如果圖案加一d曲線亦係增加水，直線就係增加土<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3UjE0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3UjE0p.jpg&h=8a017fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢面國旗就比較土屬<br />\n<br />\n如果加獅子山既線條係黑色度就會增加水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"}]}